Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放假要休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔也在外面吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我没时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 你好像一直在烦燥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,后辈下礼拜升部长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我变成他下属了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的后辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,之前有来过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到竟然被他超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,老公自尊心很强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因此大受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都帮不上他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很想帮他忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今后请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈把头抬起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这世界是结果论英雄的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待前辈的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先生的情绪变的很不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,工作也漫不经心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一方面是后辈当上部长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,另一方面是自己做不出成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的计划出问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我去一下公司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,几点回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你喜欢苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起他突然有公事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是当季 请一定要尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,亏了你还记得我喜欢吃苹果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以前常来家里吃饭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那时真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的料理是我动力源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我先生最近给你添麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,公司因为前辈的失误 有点混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我一开始就知道他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是自尊心太强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会开除他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看在你的面子上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一眼就爱上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈没办法给你幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经是人妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我所想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就交换肉体就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只会暂时麻痹而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感受我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,想这样做很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想这样做很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别脱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,常常都有梦到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,连指尖也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,julia的手好柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他不想这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想这样做很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,终于等到这个时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比想像中还棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,双柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,味道真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想这样很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,奶头也好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,像雪一样洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没看过这种美的奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别舔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很敏感喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来换这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想像很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,毛是长怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很容易湿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂的大小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是指这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,闻闻味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.38,0:22:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,腿张开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是这种人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,味道真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要有点湿了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.08,0:24:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.26,0:24:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真完美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.53,0:24:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,粉红色的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.07,0:24:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.65,0:25:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.49,0:25:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.09,0:25:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,比想像中的还棒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.54,0:25:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好珍惜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.38,0:25:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我会珍惜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.67,0:25:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.71,0:26:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别舔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.52,0:26:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小菊花也让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.18,0:27:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别掰开
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.81,0:28:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,比较看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.41,0:28:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟前辈 谁比较爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.12,0:29:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.48,0:29:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.22,0:29:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.52,0:29:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.26,0:29:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但身体有反映了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.35,0:30:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一直到你爱上我为止
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.75,0:30:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不会停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.66,0:30:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,会一直持续下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.61,0:30:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在这之后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.77,0:30:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,先生因为工作的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.21,0:30:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,已经到了崩溃的边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.80,0:31:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能会被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.05,0:31:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好想死
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.49,0:31:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次看到被对方要求撤换的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.83,0:31:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是有我在帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.10,0:31:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在搞不好真的已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.78,0:31:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.78,0:31:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,救救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.66,0:31:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 我只想跟你得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.36,0:32:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要我帮他也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.64,0:32:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你爱上我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.47,0:32:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.11,0:32:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只是形式上也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.68,0:32:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,说你爱我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.55,0:32:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.70,0:32:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算对前辈见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.64,0:32:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对你来说比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.09,0:33:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.87,0:33:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.51,0:33:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大声一点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.91,0:33:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.75,0:33:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大声一点
